### Weiyou local API smoke script
### Usage:
### 1) Start weiyou-app-server on http://localhost:8080/api
### 2) Run password login first
### 3) Paste returned accessToken into @accessToken

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@mobile = 13800000001
@password = 123456
@deviceId = device-demo-android-10001
@accessToken = paste-access-token-here
@refreshToken = paste-refresh-token-here
@conversationId = 90001
@groupConversationId = 90002
@targetUserId = 10002
@redPacketId = 81001

### Bootstrap
GET {{baseUrl}}/app/bootstrap?clientType=app&version=0.1.0

### Password login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobile": "{{mobile}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "deviceId": "{{deviceId}}"
}

### Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/token/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Current profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/profile/update
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "Micro Friend Demo",
  "city": "Shenzhen",
  "signature": "Local integration run"
}

### Device list
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/device/list
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Conversation list
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversation/list?pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Message history
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/message/history?conversationId={{conversationId}}&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Send chat message
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/message/send
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": {{conversationId}},
  "msgType": 1,
  "clientMsgId": "cmsg-local-001",
  "content": {
    "text": "hello from local http script"
  }
}

### Mark message as read
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/message/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": {{conversationId}},
  "messageId": 70002
}

### Wallet overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Wallet bills
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/bill/list?pageNo=1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Transfer to friend
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/transfer/create
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": {{targetUserId}},
  "amountFen": 100,
  "remark": "demo transfer"
}

### Create group red packet
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/red-packet/create
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amountFen": 300,
  "count": 3,
  "type": 2,
  "greeting": "good luck",
  "groupId": {{groupConversationId}}
}

### Open seeded red packet
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/red-packet/open
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "redPacketId": {{redPacketId}}
}

### Discovery features
GET {{baseUrl}}/feature/discovery?cityCode=440300
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Search suggest
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/suggest?keyword=weiyou
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Official account detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/official/account/detail?officialId=20001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Open miniapp session
POST {{baseUrl}}/miniapp/open
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appId": "miniapp-demo-001",
  "path": "/pages/index/index",
  "scene": "chat"
}

### Notice list
GET {{baseUrl}}/notice/list
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Submit feedback
POST {{baseUrl}}/feedback/create
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "demo feedback from local http script",
  "images": [],
  "contact": "demo@local"
}

### Upload policy
POST {{baseUrl}}/media/upload/policy
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bizType": "moment",
  "fileName": "demo.png",
  "contentType": "image/png"
}

### Logout current device
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "{{deviceId}}"
}

### WebSocket reference
### ws://localhost:8081/ws/chat?token=<accessToken>&deviceId=<deviceId>
### Example message:
### {"event":"MESSAGE_SEND","requestId":"ws-msg-001","data":{"conversationId":90001,"msgType":1,"content":{"text":"hello ws"}}}
